@page "/"

<PageTitle>Algorithm Visualizer - Home</PageTitle>

<div class="home-container">
    <div class="jumbotron">
        <h1>Welcome to Algorithm Visualizer</h1>
        <p class="lead">
            Explore and understand algorithms through interactive visualizations.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="algorithm-categories">
        <div class="algorithm-card">
            <a href="/pathfinding">
                <h2>Pathfinding Algorithms</h2>
                <div class="card-description">
                    <p>Visualize how algorithms like A*, Dijkstra, BFS, and DFS find paths in a grid.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Understand the differences between informed and uninformed search</li>
                        <li>See how different heuristics affect A* performance</li>
                        <li>Create custom grids with walls and weighted paths</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="algorithm-card">
            <a href="/sorting">
                <h2>Sorting Algorithms</h2>
                <div class="card-description">
                    <p>Watch how algorithms like Bubble Sort, Quick Sort, Merge Sort, and Heap Sort rearrange arrays.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Compare the performance of different sorting techniques</li>
                        <li>Understand divide and conquer sorting strategies</li>
                        <li>See how different initial conditions affect performance</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="algorithm-card">
            <a href="/trees">
                <h2>Tree Algorithms</h2>
                <div class="card-description">
                    <p>Explore operations on binary search trees like insertion, deletion, searching, and traversal.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Understand tree-based data structures</li>
                        <li>See how tree operations maintain binary search tree properties</li>
                        <li>Visualize different tree traversal methods</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="features-section">
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature">
                <span class="oi oi-eye" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <h3>Step-By-Step Visualization</h3>
                <p>Watch algorithms execute one step at a time with clear explanations</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <span class="oi oi-timer" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <h3>Performance Metrics</h3>
                <p>Compare execution time and operation counts between algorithms</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <span class="oi oi-pencil" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <h3>Interactive Editor</h3>
                <p>Create custom inputs and modify parameters in real-time</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <span class="oi oi-book" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <h3>Educational Insights</h3>
                <p>Learn about algorithm complexity, strategies, and applications</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .home-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .jumbotron {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .algorithm-categories {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 30px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .algorithm-card {
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .algorithm-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }

    .algorithm-card a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: block;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .algorithm-card h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: #3f51b5;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .card-description {
        margin-top: 15px;
    }

    .card-description ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        color: #555;
    }

    .features-section {
        margin-top: 40px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .features-section h2 {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .features-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 30px;
    }

    .feature {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .feature .oi {
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #3f51b5;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .feature h3 {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .algorithm-categories {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .features-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>